Stocks Erase Losses as Tate & Lyle, Vodafone Group, BP Decline in London

-- B y   S a r a h   J o n e s
-- 
2011-08-09T07:10:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-09/stocks-erase-losses-as-tate-lyle-vodafone-group-bp-decline-in-london.html
U.K. stocks erased losses, led by a
rally in mining companies.  The benchmark FTSE 100 Index climbed 0.5 percent to 5,094.2
at 8:08 a.m. in London, snapping a seven-day selloff.  Antofagasta Plc (ANTO) , Vedanta Resources Plc and Rio Tinto Group
all rallied more than 3 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Sarah Jones at 
 sjones35@bloomberg.net  